OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FAn ex-girlfriend of Stephen McCullagh
OL,7,Fdescribed how he hit her, threatened
OL,8,Fto burn "sentimental" belongings and
OL,9,Fsecretly recorded counselling sessions
OL,10,Fabout a stillbirth.
OL,12,FMr McCullagh, 36, of Woodland Gardens,
OL,13,FLisburn, is accused of murdering his
OL,14,Fpregnant girlfriend, Natalie McNally,
OL,15,Fin December 2022.
OL,17,FHe denies the charge.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/21
