PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FDuring his trial at Belfast Crown
OL,7,FCourt, the woman, who can not be named
OL,8,Ffor legal reasons, described how the
OL,9,Fcouple first met at the end of 2015
OL,10,Fand had an "off and on" relationship
OL,11,Fover the course of seven years.
OL,13,FOn Friday, she told the court about an
OL,14,Fincident which took place over the
OL,15,Flast two days of 2019, which
OL,16,Fculminated in her attempting to take
OL,17,Fher own life by jumping out of a car
OL,18,FMr McCullagh was driving.
OL,26,@rD@LOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/21
