FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FThe court heard the pair had been
OL,7,Fseparated, but tried to "reconcile the
OL,8,Frelationship" on December 30.
OL,10,FShe said Mr McCullagh revealed he had
OL,11,Ftried to have sex with another woman
OL,12,Fbut did not because "he said he loved
OL,13,Fme".
OL,15,FThe woman said she had issues with her
OL,16,Fphone "running slow".
OL,18,FLater, the court heard, while fixing
OL,19,Fher phone, McCullagh discovered photos
OL,20,Fand messages the woman had shared with
OL,21,Fanother man.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@MO]tD@UOUuD@CO]xD@GOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/21
