SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FWhen he discovered the images, she
OL,7,Fsaid, Mr McCullagh became angry,
OL,8,F"slammed his fist into the bed" and
OL,9,Fshouted: "Why would you do this? Why
OL,10,Fwould you do this? I thought you loved
OL,11,Fme."
OL,13,FDuring cross examination, defence
OL,14,Fbarrister John Kearney said Mr
OL,15,FMcCullagh had no recollection of
OL,16,Fpunching the bed.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]qD@JOUsD@DO]
