OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FAfter spending the night of December
OL,7,F30 together, the pair continued to
OL,8,Fargue throughout the following day,
OL,9,Fthe woman said she felt "embarrassed"
OL,10,Fshe was messaging the other man and "I
OL,11,Freally did want a relationship back
OL,12,Fwith Stephen."
OL,14,FBut she said: "There was no time while
OL,15,FI was with the defendant that I was
OL,16,Ftalking to this man."
OL,26,@qD@YOUqD@eO]rD@eOUtD@NO]vD@OOUxD@UO]
