OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FOn New Year's Eve, she said she
OL,7,Fcontinued to try "to explain myself",
OL,8,Fbut he did not want to "hear my side
OL,9,Fof the story" or "why I was messaging
OL,10,Fthis man".
OL,12,FShe added, "I think I made it worse"
OL,13,Fbecause "I went on and on and on about
OL,14,Fit".
OL,16,FThe court heard that, after he
OL,17,Freturned home from work, they
OL,18,Fcontinued to argue, and Mr McCullagh
OL,19,Fsuggested she return to her family
OL,20,Fhome, but neither of them could reach
OL,21,Fher mother to come and collect her.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@dO]pD@XOUqD@MO]qD@ROUrD@IO]tD@
OL,26,ALOUtD@dO]uD@IOUvD@CO]
