OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FThe court was told they went inside
OL,7,Fwhere the disagreement continued and,
OL,8,Fafter the woman followed Mr McCullagh
OL,9,Finto the bathroom, she said he pushed
OL,10,Fher into the bath "with his elbow"
OL,11,Fwhere she sat for "a couple of seconds
OL,12,Fin shock".
OL,14,FMr Kearney said Mr McCullagh had "no
OL,15,Frecollection" of the bath incident.
OL,26,@rD@SOUrD@bO]sD@SOUtD@IO]vD@bOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/21
