OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FShe said she made it clear to Mr
OL,7,FMcCullagh she wanted a relationship
OL,8,Fback with him and the journey
OL,9,Fcontinued towards her family home.
OL,11,FAt that stage, she said she was
OL,12,Fsuicidal and told Mr McCullagh: "I
OL,13,Fdon't want to live any more",
OL,14,Funbuckled her seatbelt and tried to
OL,15,Fopen the door and jump out.
OL,17,FThe car was moving at about 45-50
OL,18,Fmiles per hour, she said.
OL,26,@tD@aOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/21
