PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FMr McCullagh stopped the car
OL,7,F"abruptly" and pulled her back inside,
OL,8,Fshe said, at that point he began to
OL,9,Fslap her across the face and punched
OL,10,Fher on the left side of her temple.
OL,12,FThe woman said he told her, "I can
OL,13,Fkill myself in my own time" and "I
OL,14,Fdon't want this to be a murder car".
OL,16,FShe said, at the time: "I thought he
OL,17,Fwas trying to knock sense into me,
OL,18,Fbecause that is what he had said", but
OL,19,F"looking back" she "thought of it as
OL,20,Fassault".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]tD@]OUuD@[O]uD@aOUvD@cO]xD@
OL,26,AXOUzD@aO]{D@AOU{D@NO]{D@TOU|D@HO]
