OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FMr Kearney said it is "accepted" Mr
OL,7,FMcCullagh did slap her, but said he
OL,8,Fnever punched the woman and denied
OL,9,Fusing the language she described.
OL,11,FA transcript of a police interview
OL,12,Fwith Mr McCullagh about the incident
OL,13,Fwas read to the court, in which he
OL,14,Fsaid he had "never hit a woman in my
OL,15,Flife" before.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@`O]vD@MOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/21
