OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FHe described the moment the woman
OL,7,Ftried to get out of the car as
OL,8,Fhappening in an "instant" and that he
OL,9,Ftried "pulling her harder than I've
OL,10,Fever pulled" to get her to stay in the
OL,11,Fcar and that she was "crying and
OL,12,Fcrying and crying".
OL,14,FHe admitted slapping her on the back
OL,15,Fof head and back to "shock" her and
OL,16,F"make her see sense".
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@YO]qD@GOUrD@LO]sD@VOUtD@RO]wD@
OL,26,AUOUwD@[O]xD@AOUxD@TO]
