OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FHe told her "I know you have mental
OL,7,Fhealth issues" but that this was not
OL,8,Fthe way to deal with it, adding he had
OL,9,Ftried for four years to "get the right
OL,10,Fhelp she needs" from therapists.
OL,12,FAlso, during the car journey and as
OL,13,Fshe reached her family home, she said
OL,14,FMr McCullagh threatened "pretty
OL,15,Fharshly" to share the images he had
OL,16,Ffound on her phone with his family,
OL,17,Fher family and her workplace.
OL,19,FMr Kearney said the defendant denied
OL,20,Fmaking the threats.
OL,26,@nD@MOUoD@NO]qD@YOUrD@OO]vD@YOUwD@HO]
