OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FThey split after the incident and
OL,7,Fencouraged by her mother, the woman
OL,8,Freported Mr McCullagh to the police
OL,9,Fbut withdrew her statement less than
OL,10,F48 hours later, saying: "I didn't want
OL,11,Fhim to go to prison."
OL,13,FThe relationship restarted following
OL,14,Fthe pandemic and the woman said she
OL,15,Fexperienced a still birth on January 7
OL,16,F2022.
OL,18,FShe said she experienced pain that day
OL,19,Fthat she thought was from her kidneys
OL,20,Fand went to doctors who confirmed she
OL,21,Fwas pregnant.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/21
