OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772975481
OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FSaid she "wasn't coping very well" was
OL,7,F"very tearful day to day", "didn't
OL,8,Freally want to get out of bed" and was
OL,9,F"still in shock" after the loss of her
OL,10,Fchild.
OL,12,FShe was prescribed medication for her
OL,13,Fmental health issues in July 2022 and
OL,14,Fthe couple split again that month.
OL,16,FThe court heard how police contacted
OL,17,Fher in 2024 and told her some of her
OL,18,Fcounselling sessions had been recorded
OL,19,Fand found on his computers.
