OL,3,CNatalie McNally murder accused's ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend tells court he hit her
OL,6,FShe said she had not been asked if she
OL,7,Fwanted them to be recorded and did not
OL,8,Fknow they had been recorded.
OL,10,FMr Kearney said it was Mr McCullagh's
OL,11,Fcase that he had offered to tape some
OL,12,Fof the sessions because the woman had
OL,13,Ftold him she was struggling to
OL,14,Fremember what she had said during them.
OL,16,FShe replied: "He never discussed with
OL,17,Fme recording my sessions."
